metadata.name: When It Gets Dark Inside
metadata.description:
Your insecurities are your worst enemy and when you act up on it, first it will destroy everything around you, and then it will destroy you the worst.

“I'm in pain, 
wanna put ten shots in my brain
I've been trippin' 'bout some things, can't change
Suicidal, same time I'm tame
Waiting for a phone call”
-Jocelyn Flores (XXX Tentacion)
